{"tid":1718641,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果政府冷處理","createTime":"2019-11-14T01:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T02:02:19.000Z","uid":92188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"44d1338a83f2d7797390ae3df2fa14e1d85c3390","tid":1718641,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:46:56.000Z","msg":"而家佔大學其實好似佔領區，日日影響交通，但大家知香港人嘅善忘同鍾意返工嘅心<br />\n如果政府一直唔清場，一直封住吐露港<br />\n啲人有機會會開始覺得係示威者影響交通<br />\n我覺得而家要文宣返其實吐露港係可以開通，但政府唔做<br />\n而除咗中大其實其他大學唔需要特別佔<br />\n流動式快閃係會好過長期喺度，只會令到啲同學好疲累，同埋冇機會出去幫手"},{"pid":"e5be21807ffdaa42190c4ea72deb880030811030","tid":1718641,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"政府係咪想用返佔中果招"},{"pid":"62fe79db0bb25c8c2bd045c0574de340dd2d0e29","tid":1718641,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:49:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8367c570168dc5b3cf84051b2f20a15d9bde484","tid":1718641,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5be21807ffdaa42190c4ea72deb880030811030","tid":1718641,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"政府係咪想用返佔中果招"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:49:57.000Z","msg":"宜家呢個狀態應該係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4212b09d16a5f5291bdb9e48012c80a10f62669f","tid":1718641,"uid":9413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJH5eru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJH5eru.jpg&h=096e62d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcaf09f496df265013290073f94fe0de1761fbc2","tid":1718641,"uid":49016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:52:25.000Z","msg":"佢無可能冷處理到，雨傘大家只係訓醒等民主<br />\n依家香港人會自己爭取<br />\n除非佢縮到全線鐵爆左都唔理，政府機構被爆都唔理<br />\n如果唔係佢一日要出狗，一日都有犯錯機會"},{"pid":"82b1af67c39fd22785bba91ba3764c5e9e9341a1","tid":1718641,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:52:38.000Z","msg":"唔會，而家各行各業都籌旗工會。 根本黃嘅人已經唔想返工。所以唔會入雨傘"},{"pid":"0a6f695236e2a524b6381fdd8a28ae3b0bdf472a","tid":1718641,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:53:55.000Z","msg":"而家大學罷晒課，最少可以同你塞鐵兩星期，睇下邊個傷"},{"pid":"5cab2accb188a0692dd4281190da3ced626dafea","tid":1718641,"uid":326665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"昨日政府唔攻中大，因為想藉三罷等民意逆轉，如果今次大家都唔割政府真係無棋行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52b12361a93af851e352c6384a5d43b47e2530a","tid":1718641,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"冷咩處理<br />\n佔中跟本對經濟冇影響<br />\n而家係全港經濟影響<br />\n你試下咁拖三個月??"},{"pid":"ce9b9f3800d21d35e7a84d4eaf69da5f71582e3f","tid":1718641,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:55:17.000Z","msg":"其實佢地仲等緊民意逆轉，區議會搞得成起碼仲keep返部分議席，如果取消唔選亦都對佢地有利"},{"pid":"a1c205666938de188c5d78de2c8cbd3de791904d","tid":1718641,"uid":80881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8367c570168dc5b3cf84051b2f20a15d9bde484","tid":1718641,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5be21807ffdaa42190c4ea72deb880030811030","tid":1718641,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"政府係咪想用返佔中果招"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:49:57.000Z","msg":"宜家呢個狀態應該係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:56:08.000Z","msg":"而家先第四日邊算，況且其他地方都仲打緊"},{"pid":"a34010c9ca135770607bbc91000d7d25c8abcd26","tid":1718641,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:02:19.000Z","msg":"文宣，政府唔做嘢，任由道路封閉，影響市面"}]}